---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Certificates & Quality Assurance" description="UE Chemicals quality certifications, ISO standards, COA, SDS & TDS documentation. REACH-compliant chemical supply from Essen, Germany." activePage="certificates">

  <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Quality Assurance</div>
      <h1>Certificates &amp; Quality</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Every chemical we supply meets the highest purity standards, backed by rigorous quality control and full documentation.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== QUALITY OVERVIEW ========== -->
  <section class="qa-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="qa-overview-grid">
        <div class="qa-overview-text">
          <div class="section-label">Our Commitment</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Quality You Can Verify</h2>
          <p>At UE Chemicals, quality is not a marketing claim — it is a measurable, documented fact. Every batch of product that leaves our facility in Essen, Germany is accompanied by a full suite of analytical documentation, so you can independently verify exactly what you are receiving.</p>
          <p>Our quality management system covers the entire supply chain: raw material sourcing, in-house purification and processing, analytical testing, packaging, storage, and hazmat-compliant shipping. We maintain stringent protocols at every stage to guarantee consistency, purity, and safety.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-overview-stats">
          <div class="qa-stat">
            <div class="qa-stat-num">99.999%</div>
            <div class="qa-stat-label">Maximum Purity Grade (5N)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qa-stat">
            <div class="qa-stat-num">100%</div>
            <div class="qa-stat-label">Orders with COA Included</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qa-stat">
            <div class="qa-stat-num">REACH</div>
            <div class="qa-stat-label">EU Regulation Compliant</div>
          </div>
          <div class="qa-stat">
            <div class="qa-stat-num">ISO</div>
            <div class="qa-stat-label">Certified Quality Processes</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== CERTIFICATIONS ========== -->
  <section class="qa-certs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Standards &amp; Certifications</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Certified Quality Management</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--text-secondary);">Our operations comply with internationally recognized standards for quality, environmental management, and occupational safety.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="qa-certs-grid">
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-award"></i></div>
          <h4>ISO 9001:2015</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">Quality Management System</p>
          <p>Our quality management system is certified to ISO 9001:2015, ensuring consistent product quality, customer satisfaction, and continuous improvement across all processes — from procurement to delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i></div>
          <h4>ISO 14001:2015</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">Environmental Management System</p>
          <p>We operate an environmental management system certified to ISO 14001:2015, minimizing environmental impact through responsible chemical handling, waste management, and emissions control at our Essen facility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
          <h4>ISO 45001:2018</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">Occupational Health &amp; Safety</p>
          <p>Employee and customer safety is paramount. Our ISO 45001-certified occupational health and safety management system ensures safe chemical handling, storage, and transport procedures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask-vial"></i></div>
          <h4>REACH Compliance</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">EU Regulation (EC) No. 1907/2006</p>
          <p>All products are fully compliant with the EU REACH regulation. Substances are registered and documented according to European Chemical Agency (ECHA) requirements for safe use and market access within the EU.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i></div>
          <h4>CLP Regulation</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">Classification, Labelling &amp; Packaging</p>
          <p>Products are classified, labelled, and packaged in full compliance with CLP Regulation (EC) No. 1272/2008, including GHS-compliant hazard pictograms, signal words, and safety statements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-cert-card">
          <div class="qa-cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></div>
          <h4>ADR / IMDG Certified</h4>
          <p class="qa-cert-full">Dangerous Goods Transport</p>
          <p>All shipments comply with ADR (road transport) and IMDG (sea transport) regulations for dangerous goods. Proper UN packaging, hazard labelling, and transport documentation included with every order.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== DOCUMENTATION ========== -->
  <section class="qa-docs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Product Documentation</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Documents Included with Every Order</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="qa-docs-grid">
        <div class="qa-doc-card">
          <div class="qa-doc-header">
            <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
            <h4>Certificate of Analysis (COA)</h4>
          </div>
          <p>Batch-specific analytical report detailing purity measurements, trace element composition, density readings, and other physical properties. Independently verified by our in-house laboratory.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Purity / Assay percentage</li>
            <li>Trace impurity analysis (ppm levels)</li>
            <li>Density and physical property verification</li>
            <li>Batch number and production date</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-doc-card">
          <div class="qa-doc-header">
            <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
            <h4>Safety Data Sheet (SDS)</h4>
          </div>
          <p>Comprehensive 16-section Safety Data Sheet compliant with EU Regulation (EC) No. 1907/2006, Annex II. Provided in the buyer's preferred language upon request.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Hazard identification &amp; classifications</li>
            <li>First-aid, firefighting &amp; spill measures</li>
            <li>Handling, storage &amp; exposure controls</li>
            <li>Toxicological &amp; ecological data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-doc-card">
          <div class="qa-doc-header">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
            <h4>Technical Data Sheet (TDS)</h4>
          </div>
          <p>Detailed specification sheet outlining physical and chemical properties, recommended applications, storage conditions, and compatibility information for each product.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Chemical formula &amp; CAS number</li>
            <li>Physical properties (density, boiling point, etc.)</li>
            <li>Recommended applications &amp; use cases</li>
            <li>Storage &amp; shelf life information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== QC PROCESS ========== -->
  <section class="qa-process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Quality Control</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Quality Control Process</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="qa-process-steps">
        <div class="qa-process-step">
          <div class="qa-process-num">01</div>
          <div class="qa-process-content">
            <h4>Raw Material Inspection</h4>
            <p>All incoming raw materials undergo rigorous inspection and testing before acceptance. Only materials meeting our strict purity thresholds enter the production pipeline.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-process-step">
          <div class="qa-process-num">02</div>
          <div class="qa-process-content">
            <h4>Processing &amp; Purification</h4>
            <p>Advanced purification and processing techniques including multi-stage distillation and filtration ensure final product purity reaches 99.99% (4N) to 99.999% (5N) grade.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-process-step">
          <div class="qa-process-num">03</div>
          <div class="qa-process-content">
            <h4>Analytical Testing</h4>
            <p>Every production batch is tested in our analytical laboratory. We measure purity, density, trace impurities, and physical properties, comparing results against our product specifications.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-process-step">
          <div class="qa-process-num">04</div>
          <div class="qa-process-content">
            <h4>Documentation &amp; Release</h4>
            <p>Only batches that pass all quality checks are released for sale. Certificate of Analysis (COA), SDS, and TDS are generated before packaging and shipping.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-process-step">
          <div class="qa-process-num">05</div>
          <div class="qa-process-content">
            <h4>Packaging &amp; Shipping QA</h4>
            <p>Products are packaged in UN-rated containers compliant with ADR and IMDG standards. Final packaging inspection ensures labelling, sealing, and documentation are correct before dispatch.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== CTA ========== -->
  <section class="qa-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="qa-cta-inner">
        <h2>Need Documentation or Have Quality Questions?</h2>
        <p>Request sample COA, SDS, or TDS before placing your order. Our technical team is happy to provide documentation or answer any quality-related inquiries.</p>
        <div class="qa-cta-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white">Request Documentation <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          <a href="/products" class="btn btn-outline-white">Browse Products <i class="fas fa-flask"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Overview ===== */
  .qa-overview { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--bg); }
  .qa-overview-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
  .qa-overview-text p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .qa-overview-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .qa-stat { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; }
  .qa-stat-num { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .qa-stat-label { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ===== Certs ===== */
  .qa-certs { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .qa-certs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
  .qa-cert-card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 30px; transition: all .3s; }
  .qa-cert-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .qa-cert-icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(var(--accent-rgb), .1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .qa-cert-card h4 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .qa-cert-full { color: var(--accent); font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .qa-cert-card p:last-child { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-size: .93rem; }

  /* ===== Documentation ===== */
  .qa-docs { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--bg); }
  .qa-docs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
  .qa-doc-card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 30px; }
  .qa-doc-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .qa-doc-header i { font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .qa-doc-header h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .qa-doc-card > p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-size: .93rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .qa-doc-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .qa-doc-card ul li { padding: 8px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: .9rem; padding-left: 20px; position: relative; }
  .qa-doc-card ul li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ===== Process ===== */
  .qa-process { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .qa-process-steps { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .qa-process-step { display: flex; gap: 30px; padding: 30px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .qa-process-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .qa-process-num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); min-width: 60px; }
  .qa-process-content h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .qa-process-content p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-size: .93rem; }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .qa-cta { padding: 90px 0; }
  .qa-cta-inner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark, #0a0f1e)); padding: 60px; border-radius: 24px; text-align: center; }
  .qa-cta-inner h2 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .qa-cta-inner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .qa-cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .qa-overview-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .qa-certs-grid, .qa-docs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .qa-certs-grid, .qa-docs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .qa-cta-inner { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .qa-process-step { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  }
</style>
